        {
            "id": 6011133,
            "title": "匯損傷！第一金5月獲利年月雙減 前5月累計仍破百億達112億 EPS 0.8元  ",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>自四月美國對等關稅衝擊全球，第二季金融市場表現動盪，第一金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2892:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2892\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2892-TW</a>) 今 (6) 公布 5 月份單月盈餘表現持穩，稅後淨利 20 億元，月減 1.9%。旗艦子公司第一銀行動能仍維持，人壽子公司獲利則受匯率劇烈波動影響而出現損失。累計前 5 月稅後淨利達 112.45 億元，年減 1.7%，每股稅後盈餘 (EPS) 為 0.80 元。 </p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011133%2Fl%2Fde0a8449d1885996227363935233dfdc.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011133%2Fl%2Fde0a8449d1885996227363935233dfdc.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011133%2Fl%2Fde0a8449d1885996227363935233dfdc.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011133%2Fl%2Fde0a8449d1885996227363935233dfdc.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011133%2Fl%2Fde0a8449d1885996227363935233dfdc.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011133%2Fl%2Fde0a8449d1885996227363935233dfdc.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011133%2Fl%2Fde0a8449d1885996227363935233dfdc.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011133%2Fl%2Fde0a8449d1885996227363935233dfdc.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011133%2Fl%2Fde0a8449d1885996227363935233dfdc.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011133%2Fl%2Fde0a8449d1885996227363935233dfdc.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011133%2Fl%2Fde0a8449d1885996227363935233dfdc.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011133%2Fl%2Fde0a8449d1885996227363935233dfdc.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011133%2Fl%2Fde0a8449d1885996227363935233dfdc.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011133%2Fl%2Fde0a8449d1885996227363935233dfdc.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011133%2Fl%2Fde0a8449d1885996227363935233dfdc.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011133%2Fl%2Fde0a8449d1885996227363935233dfdc.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011133%2Fl%2Fde0a8449d1885996227363935233dfdc.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">匯率衝擊第一金5月獲利年月雙減 前5月累計仍破百億達112億 EPS 0.8元 。（鉅亨網資料照）</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>第一銀行 5 月稅後盈餘為 23.04 億元，月增 4.7%，增加之核心業務獲利雖被略高之提存所抵銷，但整體獲利動能不減。呆帳覆蓋率上升至 819.39%，逾放比則維持在 0.17%。累計稅後淨利達 112.85 億元，年增 4.7%，一銀 5 月及前 5 月累計更勝集團整體表現，可以說是「一個人救全村」。  </p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>第一金證券受惠於亮眼投資收益，帶動 5 月單月盈餘上揚至 0.36 億元，月增 672.2%。累計稅後淨利達 1.60 億元，年減 67.9%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>第一金人壽 5 月受<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>匯率衝擊最明顯，震盪的匯市進一步導致人壽匯損擴大，單月損失達 3.35 億元。累計稅後淨利由正轉負，計虧損達 0.79 億元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
