        {
            "id": 6011179,
            "title": "兆豐金5月獲利年月雙增續稱霸 前5月賺133.65億元年減2成 EPS 0.9元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>公股金控龍頭兆豐金（2886-TW）今（6）日公告 5 月自結盈餘，單月稅後盈餘 31.84 億元，月增 46.66%，年增 13.59%，呈現年月雙增；累計今年前 5 月稅後盈餘為 133.65 億元，年減 21.02%，每股盈餘（EPS）達 0.9 元，暫居公股金控第一。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011179%2Fl%2Fbca118e6b43afe07ef4285c342bb9803.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011179%2Fl%2Fbca118e6b43afe07ef4285c342bb9803.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011179%2Fl%2Fbca118e6b43afe07ef4285c342bb9803.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011179%2Fl%2Fbca118e6b43afe07ef4285c342bb9803.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011179%2Fl%2Fbca118e6b43afe07ef4285c342bb9803.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011179%2Fl%2Fbca118e6b43afe07ef4285c342bb9803.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011179%2Fl%2Fbca118e6b43afe07ef4285c342bb9803.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011179%2Fl%2Fbca118e6b43afe07ef4285c342bb9803.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011179%2Fl%2Fbca118e6b43afe07ef4285c342bb9803.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011179%2Fl%2Fbca118e6b43afe07ef4285c342bb9803.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011179%2Fl%2Fbca118e6b43afe07ef4285c342bb9803.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011179%2Fl%2Fbca118e6b43afe07ef4285c342bb9803.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011179%2Fl%2Fbca118e6b43afe07ef4285c342bb9803.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011179%2Fl%2Fbca118e6b43afe07ef4285c342bb9803.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011179%2Fl%2Fbca118e6b43afe07ef4285c342bb9803.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011179%2Fl%2Fbca118e6b43afe07ef4285c342bb9803.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011179%2Fl%2Fbca118e6b43afe07ef4285c342bb9803.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">兆豐金5月獲利年月雙增續稱霸 前5月賺133.65億元 EPS 0.9元 。（圖：兆豐金提供）</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>5 月獲利動能主要來自旗下兆豐銀行，受惠股市反彈及財務操作收益回升，單月稅後盈餘達 27.89 億元，月增 28.47%；累計前 5 月稅後盈餘達 121.51 億元，雖較去年同期減少 19.12%，但減幅主因是去年同期挹注高鐵聯貸案利息補償金，基期偏高所致。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>銀行高層表示，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>匯率自 5 月暴力升值，壽險業首當其衝，但對銀行業反是利多，因可受惠於換匯業務，增加手收。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>其餘子公司表現，兆豐票券前 5 月稅後盈餘 9.68 億元；兆豐證券受惠 5 月股市表現，自營與承銷業務由虧轉盈，累計稅後盈餘 2.91 億元；兆豐產險貢獻 2.73 億元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
